<para>List of contexts. Contexts are configured using <ref refid="group__ztest__ztress_1gabab05b8db44a7024ce23cb34bf999e42" kindref="member">ZTRESS_TIMER</ref> and <ref refid="group__ztest__ztress_1gaed561641541e8ced6866f2f1227f21c0" kindref="member">ZTRESS_THREAD</ref> macros. <ref refid="group__ztest__ztress_1gabab05b8db44a7024ce23cb34bf999e42" kindref="member">ZTRESS_TIMER</ref> must be the first argument if used. Each thread context has an assigned priority. The priority is assigned in a descending order (first listed thread context has the highest priority). The maximum number of supported thread contexts, including the timer context, is configurable in Kconfig (ZTRESS_MAX_THREADS). </para>
